         <abstract id="aspace_20a7ce34fcf6da178bf7d57ec59ee38e">The records consist of files of Philip K. Bondy, professor in the Yale School of Medicine, concerning the Department of Internal Medicine; Yale's relation to the Veteran's Administration Hospital in West Haven, Connecticut; and other administrative matters.</abstract>
